### API para Control de Medicamentos - Ejemplos de Uso

### 1. Obtener todos los medicamentos
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Obtener medicamentos con paginación
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications?limit=5&offset=0
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Obtener medicamento por ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Crear nuevo medicamento
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Aspirina 100mg",
  "description": "Analgésico y antiagregante plaquetario para el alivio del dolor y la prevención de eventos cardiovasculares",
  "active_ingredient": "Ácido acetilsalicílico",
  "dosage_form": "Tableta",
  "strength": "100mg",
  "manufacturer": "Genérico",
  "batch_number": "BATCH011",
  "expiry_date": "2026-12-31",
  "quantity": 200,
  "storage_conditions": "Almacenar en lugar seco y fresco, protegido de la luz"
}

### 5. Actualizar medicamento completo
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Paracetamol 500mg Actualizado",
  "description": "Analgésico y antipirético para el alivio del dolor y la fiebre - Versión actualizada",
  "active_ingredient": "Paracetamol",
  "dosage_form": "Tableta",
  "strength": "500mg",
  "manufacturer": "Genérico Plus",
  "batch_number": "BATCH001",
  "expiry_date": "2025-12-31",
  "quantity": 175,
  "storage_conditions": "Almacenar en lugar seco y fresco, protegido de la luz, temperatura ambiente"
}

### 6. Actualizar solo la cantidad
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/1/quantity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 125
}

### 7. Buscar medicamentos
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/search?q=paracetamol
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Buscar por ingrediente activo
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/search?q=ibuprofeno
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Obtener medicamentos próximos a vencer (30 días por defecto)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/expiring-soon
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Obtener medicamentos próximos a vencer (60 días)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/expiring-soon?days=60
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Obtener medicamentos con stock bajo (10 por defecto)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/low-stock
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. Obtener medicamentos con stock bajo (umbral personalizado)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/low-stock?threshold=50
Content-Type: application/json

### 13. Eliminar medicamento
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/medications/1
Content-Type: application/json

